43
00:06:11,080 --> 00:06:12,718
How long have we known each other?

44
00:06:13,880 --> 00:06:15,598
A long time.

45
00:06:15,760 --> 00:06:17,512
l've forgotten.

46
00:06:26,280 --> 00:06:28,120
